Wiki Updates:

Changelog:
* Updated to support CB 1.4.5-R1 and and CB 1.4.6-R0.1
* Added gate countdowns to delay teleporting. New gate options "countdown", "countdownInterval", "countdownFormat", "countdownIntervalFormat", "countdownCancelFormat".
* Added support for BungeeCord server proxy. See [[BungeeCord]] for more information.
* Fixed building gates from inventory to handle signs correctly.
